title: Episode 55 Ft. YG

description:
Get ready for YG's new guaranteed classic album "Still Brazy" and now hear his classic Lip Service sit-down with Angela Yee, Stephanie Santiago and Gigi Maguire. YG loosens up as they discuss calling your woman a bitch, the importance of marriage, and then play their own version of Scruples. Would you have sex with a virgin?
